{"tid":1589153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣細節求指導","createTime":"2019-09-23T07:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T07:45:31.000Z","uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95803539987d945e05db55d3369f57addeaacaa4","tid":1589153,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"按照近來政府嘅套路，加上一啲人士嘅言論，<br />\n我相信政府依家係致力減少示威者嘅支持度，<br />\n所以我相信，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳點解要支持抗爭者，比宣傳點解黑警暴力，更重要</span>，<br />\n以下想睇下大家有冇更多嘅意見，<br />\n方便我哋集中資源，聚焦反擊政府嘅宣傳工作。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">若想支持 Facebook 落廣告，請考慮參加眾籌。(進度：$900/30,000)<br />\n反送中社交媒體落廣告計劃（第一期眾籌） <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1580258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1580258</a></span></em>"},{"pid":"2afa1ea9b62c6e6c74a0059620a8090826be7299","tid":1589153,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"5861c4c9f15227a203a5d9593276ec43ef199d38","tid":1589153,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f19f183d1d3e5edb6432c888359818095bb3aed","tid":1589153,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>十一國殤 全民黑衣</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ishNdyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FishNdyx.jpg&h=21d2a745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTDkyyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTDkyyx.jpg&h=565c80c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5c2549745623d71038dd85c62af651be7370e5e",